# shared/ is source-only (no build step), so there are no package-specific
# artifacts to ignore here — node_modules, coverage and *.tsbuildinfo are all
# covered by the root .gitignore.
#
# This file exists only so the convention (a .gitignore per package) is
# consistent. Add entries here only if something is generated *inside* shared/
# that the root file doesn't already cover.